<item>
            <title>[LU-12629] large CPU usage during obdecho-survey test</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12629</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Large CPU usage found during obdecho-survey test. Based on profiling, page allocation is result of it. Looking in lustre logs, lu_env used to store paged don&apos;t reused and allocated for each call. as obdecho env already uses an CL tag, it good to reuse a cl env cache as similar as does for md operations.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
